title: I am cursed
body:
Every game I play, I lose.

for every single GD reltated game... was on the losing team, I was generally a non-factor because everyone else carried while I either did not get kills, or died, or just got some assists.... every game had 1 lane where it was a blow out, then my "hey i'm doing okay ish!" turns to utter failure

every game.

#LoLElephantCurse
